      public Food(String itemName, String itemLocation, boolean unique, String description, int healthValue, int livesAdded, boolean perishable)
      Creates a new food with the given itemName, itemLocation, unique, description, healthValue, livesAdded, and perishable
      Parameters:
      itemName - the name of the item
      itemLocation - the location of the item
      unique - determines if the item is unique
      description - the use of the item
      healthValue - determines if the item is hidden
      livesAdded - the lives added from the food
      perishable - determines if the food is perishable
